          <div class="bg-purple/10 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full mb-6 mx-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-purple" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Member Communication Teams</h3>
          <p class="text-grey">Focus on presenting information clearly, backed by accurate underlying calculations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-brand text-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Ready to transform your member benefit statements?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">Contact us today to discuss how we can help you provide accurate, consistent information to your members</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn bg-white text-navy hover:bg-white/90">Start a conversation today!</a>
